trends: There has been one other sighting in Englewood
There were no other sightings in Englewood on or around September 13th 2010
divs: Sighting DetailsLast week or so I wrote about a star-like object dancing and chaging colors and eventually moving west.... it's back. It's relatively in the same spot and I have been watching for it every night. This is the first time it has been back. Only one night was not clear, so I'm certain it was not there between the first sighting and now. Just wanted to document this. It definately is moveing around - left, right, up, down... not plane or helicopter like at all.
Summary: It's back! That star-like object dancing and changing colors.
